Product Version     25.10    Cadence Design Systems, Inc.
timing_derate..._compatibility(25.10)    timing_derate..._compatibility(25.10)

Name
       timing_derate_negative_delay_backward_compatibility

Syntax
       timing_derate_negative_delay_backward_compatibility {true | false}

       Default: true

       Controls the effective derate calculation for negative delays. When ef-
       fective derate is requested for negative delays, the value will be con-
       verted  according  to  the negative delay scaling rule, e.g., 2 - posi-
       tiveVal.

       To set this global variable, use the set command.

